OL,3,CWhy is the South West building so many
OL,4,Cnew homes when thousands are empty?
OL,6,FThe roof was falling in, water was
OL,7,Fcreeping into the adjoining houses,
OL,8,Fand the garden was a jungle. No one
OL,9,Fhad lived in the two-bedroom terraced
OL,10,Fhouse in Bath's Oldfield Park since
OL,11,F2001.
OL,13,FYet Bath & North East Somerset Council
OL,14,Fcould do little about it, even though
OL,15,Fit had a housing waiting list of 5,500
OL,16,Fpeople.
OL,18,F"There's no specific, standalone law
OL,19,Fthat prohibits a property being left
OL,20,Fempty," says Debbie Freeman, the
OL,21,Fcouncil's sole Empty Property Officer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
