OL,3,CWhy is the South West building so many
OL,4,Cnew homes when thousands are empty?
OL,6,FThey used to have. Between 2012 and
OL,7,F2015 English councils got ring-fenced
OL,8,Fgovernment money under the National
OL,9,FEmpty Homes Programme to fill up empty
OL,10,Fhouses. They could spend it on
OL,11,Fofficers like Debbie, grants,
OL,12,Frenovations. But when the money
OL,13,Fstopped, so did much of the work.
