OL,3,CWhy is the South West building so many
OL,4,Cnew homes when thousands are empty?
OL,6,FAccording to the campaign group Action
OL,7,Fon Empty Homes, the number of long-
OL,8,Fterm empty properties in England
OL,9,Fjumped by a third once the programme
OL,10,Fended.
OL,12,FIt now stands at over 265,000 empty
OL,13,Fhomes: 24,000 of them here in the
OL,14,FSouth West - these are unoccupied,
OL,15,Funfurnished homes that have stood
OL,16,Fempty for more than six months.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
