OL,3,CWhy is the South West building so many
OL,4,Cnew homes when thousands are empty?
OL,6,FCouncils do have some tools for
OL,7,Fdealing with them. They can charge
OL,8,Fextra council tax on vacant properties
OL,9,F(assuming they know who owns them -
OL,10,Fanother challenge). They can give
OL,11,Fgrants and VAT discounts to people
OL,12,Fwanting to renovate. Or they can do
OL,13,Fwhat B&NES Council does, and fight
OL,14,Fcourt battles.
OL,16,FBut there is no legal requirement for
OL,17,Flocal authorities to bring empty
OL,18,Fproperties back into use. With
OL,19,Fstretched budgets, many don't.
