OL,3,CWhy is the South West building so many
OL,4,Cnew homes when thousands are empty?
OL,6,F"Empty homes are an opportunity to
OL,7,Fdeal with the worst aspects of our
OL,8,Fhousing crisis", says Chris Bailey,
OL,9,FCampaign Manager at Action on Empty
OL,10,FHomes. "Don't leave homes empty when
OL,11,Fthey could be housing people.
OL,13,F"They're homes that are in the right
OL,14,Fplaces. They're homes that are on your
OL,15,Fstreet and my street. They're not
OL,16,Fbuilt on greenbelt. They're right
OL,17,Fthere where people want to live - in
OL,18,Fthe middle of our towns and cities -
OL,19,Fand they're going to waste."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
