OL,3,CWhy is the South West building so many
OL,4,Cnew homes when thousands are empty?
OL,6,FThe government didn't mention empty
OL,7,Fhomes in its manifesto, and it has not
OL,8,Ftalked of reviving the funding to
OL,9,Ftackle the problem. Instead it has
OL,10,Fpromised to build 1.5 million new
OL,11,Fhouses over this parliament.
OL,13,FLegally, it's the easier solution.
OL,14,FPolitically, it's powerful. But
OL,15,Fthousands of old homes stand silent
OL,16,Fand forgotten.
